Title: CCM Jetspeed FT6Pro Hockey skates size 8 regular.
Text:
Up for grabs is pair of CCM Jetspeed FT6Pro hockey skates in size 8 regular fit. Used for 5 games. Comes with box, new unused insoles and 2 sets of laces. Black steel blades. Only sharpened ever to 5/8’s
Tore my hamstring so I won’t be using them the rest of the season.
$1299.99+ taxes in stores.
$700.00 takes them!!
